      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 7 初六</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 7 初六</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初六，師出以律，否臧，凶。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first SIX, divided, shows the host going forth according to the rules (for such a movement). If these be not good, there will be evil.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
