      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 7 九二</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 7 九二</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九二，在師中吉，无咎；王三錫命。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second NINE, undivided, shows (the leader) in the midst of the host. There will be good fortune and no error. The king has thrice conveyed to him the orders (of his favour).</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
