      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 7 六三</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六三，師或輿尸，凶。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third SIX, divided, shows how the host may, possibly, have many inefficient leaders. There will be evil.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
