      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 7 上六</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 7 上六</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>上六，大君有命，開國承家，小人勿用。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The topmost SIX, divided, shows the great ruler delivering his charges, (appointing some) to be rulers of states, and others to undertake the headship of clans; but small men should not be employed (in such positions).</seg>
      </tuv>
